Brown & Lomb Inc. Dem say di pharmaceutical subsidiary agree to supply collagen shield for animal eye surgery to unit of International Minerals and Chemical Corp.

Dem no reveal term.

Di agreement na for di first time wen Bausch & Lomb go sell eye care products wey doctor dey give dem.

Di collagen shield dey help di cornea quick heal after di operation.

Di product na Pitman-Moore Inc wey be subsidiary of International Minerals.

